</p>
<p>99.6.<b> Conclude the process leading to the adoption of the bill which seeks to 
incorporate femicide in the Criminal Code (Peru);</b> 
</p>
<p>99.7.<b> Continue to improve its domestic framework for the empowerment of 
women (Singapore); 
</b></p>
<p>99.8.<b> Transpose thoroughly and implement child legislation at the provincial 
level (Portugal); 
</b></p>
