</b></p>
<p>99.17.<b> Continue to implement programmes and measures intended to 
guarantee the right to health and the right to education (Cuba); 
</b></p>
<p>99.18.<b> Continue efforts to provide attention to the most disadvantaged sectors 
(Cuba); 
</b></p>
